    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "Look, I'll be straight with you. We've got three other manufacturers hitting us up for this specific grade of steel today and our current stock is moving fast. I can hold this quote for you for the next 24 hours, but after that, price is gonna jump based on the new market rates. Do you want to lock this in now or should I move to the next guy?",
